descriptionNullable:
This is a random engagement between Byakuya and some others. I picked this up from a random website that posted an online playthrough. 
It was impossible to find a transcript of the game, so I had to settle with copying and pasting any lines I wanted/needed from the playthrough and into a document. 
I then used some lines I copied and put them into a little csv just to test it out and make sure that I did it correctly.
Use this for whatever you want, but I'll most likely be posting a larger one soon.
